Package: quickplot
Title: Create quick data exploration ggplot2 plots ready for reports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Erick I.", "Navarro-Delgado", , "ericknadel98@ciencias.unam.mx", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5147-4711"))
Description: A developing set of plot functions based on ggplot2. You choose a function, provide a tidy dataset, denote the variables, and it produces data exploration aesthetic plots ready for reports. 
